---
import SectionHeader from "./SectionHeader.astro";
---

<section class="py-12 sm:py-16 border-b-3 border-ink reveal" id="publication" data-reveal="scale-up">
  <SectionHeader num="04" title="Research" />

  <p class="mb-6 max-w-[700px] text-[15px] leading-[1.7] text-ink-soft">
    Most of my time goes into building things, but I spent part of university
    researching why ML models break under adversarial conditions.
  </p>

  <div class="flex flex-col gap-1.5">
    <a
      href="https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/9874139"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      data-cursor-label="Read"
      class="card-pressable group flex justify-between items-center border-3 border-ink px-4 sm:px-7 py-5 sm:py-5.5 bg-bg-card transition-[transform,border-color] duration-300 ease-smooth hover:translate-x-1.5 hover:border-accent no-underline text-inherit focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-accent"
    >
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-1 sm:gap-4">
        <span class="font-mono text-[11px] text-ink-muted sm:min-w-[72px]">
          Sep 2022
        </span>
        <div>
          <span class="font-serif text-lg sm:text-[22px] font-normal italic block">
            RegWeight: Adversarial Training based on Dynamically-Adjusted Regularization Weights
          </span>
          <span class="font-mono text-[11px] text-ink-muted mt-1 block">
            2022 8th International Conference on Big Data and Information Analytics (BigDIA)
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <span class="text-xl text-ink-muted transition-[transform,color] duration-300 ease-smooth group-hover:translate-x-1.5 group-hover:text-accent shrink-0 ml-4">
        →
      </span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
